---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Quoter"
  description="How Quoter handles the information you give it."
>
  <main class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="legal-panel rounded-3xl p-7 sm:p-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-[14px] font-medium text-brand-600 hover:underline">&larr; Back to Quoter</a>

      <h1 class="font-display mt-5 text-[clamp(1.9rem,5vw,2.6rem)] leading-[1.05] text-ink">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[13px] text-muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        To give you an estimate, we use the address you type in. You do not
        need to give us your name, phone number, or email just to see a price.
      </p>

      <h2>If you book an inspection</h2>
      <p>
        If you choose to book a free inspection, we ask for contact details so
        a local roofer can arrange the visit. We share those details with that
        roofer and no one else.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do not do</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell your information. We do not send marketing you did not
        ask for. We do not pass your details to call centres.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use basic, privacy-respecting analytics to understand how the site
        performs, such as page speed measurements. These do not identify you
        personally.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        If you want anything you have given us removed, email us and we will
        delete it: <a href="mailto:hello@quoter.app" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">hello@quoter.app</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-panel {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(1.3);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(1.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-float);
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 1.9rem;
  }
  p {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
</style>
